fields.title: Procurement Management System
fields.description:
We are seeking a skilled and passionate Procurement Management System to join our team on a freelance basis. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in web development, with a portfolio that demonstrates experience in creating user-friendly, visually appealing, and functional websites for non-profit organizations.

Responsibilities:
- Collaborate with our team to understand the needs and goals of our charity.
- Design and develop a responsive, accessible, and secure website.
- Implement features such as donation forms, event calendars, and volunteer sign-up sheets.
- Optimize the website for search engines to increase visibility.
- Provide maintenance and updates to the website as needed.

fields.title: Figma-Aligned Static React.js Card Component
fields.description:
I'm seeking a skilled React.js developer to create a static card component, aligned with a specific Figma design. The card will primarily serve the purpose of displaying information.

Key Requirements:
- Proficiency in React.js
- Experience in translating Figma designs into functional components
- Ability to create a responsive, static component

The ideal professional will be able to deliver a high-quality, Figma-aligned React.js card component that meets these specifications.
